<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Loan Default Notice</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c62828 0%, #b71c1c 100%);
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            margin: -20px -20px 30px -20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .status-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 0 20px 20px 20px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .default-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffcdd2 0%, #ffebee 100%);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border: 3px solid #c62828;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #b71c1c;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .default-status {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #b71c1c;
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .details {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .details .row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .details .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #666;
        }
        .details .value {
            color: #333;
        }
        .contact-button {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c62828 0%, #b71c1c 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .consequences {
            background: #fff9c4;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f57c00;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="status-icon">üö®</div>
            <h1>Loan Default Notice</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{customerName}}</strong>,</p>

            <div class="default-box">
                <div class="default-status">Account in Default</div>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0;">Your loan has been marked as defaulted due to non-payment</p>
                <div class="amount">{{totalDefaultAmount}} RWF</div>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0; font-size: 14px;"><strong>{{daysInDefault}} days past due</strong></p>
            </div>

            <h3>Default Account Details</h3>
            <div class="details">
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Loan Number:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{loanNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Default Date:</span>
                    <span class="value"><strong>{{defaultDate}}</strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Days in Default:</span>
                    <span class="value"><strong style="color: #b71c1c;">{{daysInDefault}} days</strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Total Amount Due:</span>
                    <span class="value"><strong>{{totalDefaultAmount}} RWF</strong></span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Principal Outstanding:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{principalOutstanding}} RWF</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Interest & Penalties:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{interestAndPenalties}} RWF</span>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <span class="label">Original Due Date:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{originalDueDate}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="background: #ffcdd2; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border: 2px solid #c62828;">
                <p style="margin-top: 0;"><strong>üö® Critical Account Status</strong></p>
                <p>This is a formal notice that your loan account has entered default status due to payment being overdue for more than 30 days. Immediate action is required.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="consequences">
                <p style="margin-top: 0;"><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Consequences of Default:</strong></p>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li><strong>Credit Score:</strong> Severely impacted, making future borrowing difficult</li>
                    <li><strong>Credit Limit:</strong> Suspended until full repayment</li>
                    <li><strong>Late Fees:</strong> Additional penalties continue to accrue</li>
                    <li><strong>Collections:</strong> Your account has been referred to our collections department</li>
                    <li><strong>Legal Action:</strong> May be pursued to recover outstanding amounts</li>
                    <li><strong>Credit Bureau Reporting:</strong> Default status reported to credit bureaus</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <a href="{{contactUrl}}" class="contact-button">Contact Us Immediately</a>

            <p style="background: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <strong>üí° Resolution Options:</strong><br>
                We understand that financial difficulties can arise. Please contact our collections team immediately to:<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Discuss payment arrangements<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Explore restructuring options<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Set up a repayment plan<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Avoid further legal action
            </p>

            <p style="background: #fff3e0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <strong>üìû Urgent Contact Required:</strong><br>
                Collections Department: {{collectionsPhone}}<br>
                Email: {{collectionsEmail}}<br>
                Office Hours: Monday - Friday, 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM
            </p>

            <p><strong>Important:</strong> This is a formal legal notice. Failure to respond or make payment arrangements may result in escalated collection activities and legal proceedings.</p>

            <p>We encourage you to contact us immediately to resolve this matter and minimize further consequences to your credit profile.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Credit Jambo Ltd - Collections Department</strong></p>
            <p>This is a formal legal notice regarding your defaulted loan account.</p>
            <p>Reference Number: {{loanNumber}} | Default Date: {{defaultDate}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
